===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|en|/ˈɪɡni.əs/}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj|-}}

# Pertaining to or having the nature of fire; containing fire; resembling fire.
#: ''The stone had an '''igneous''' appearance.''
# {{lb|en|geology}} Resulting from, or produced by, great heat. With rocks, it could also mean formed from lava or magma.
#: ''Granite and basalt are '''igneous''' rocks.''

